snippet.title: The Blackout Club – Announce Teaser | Question
snippet.description:
New Co-Op Horror game pits you and your friends as a group of teenagers uncovering a small-town conspiracy. From @Question_Games, makers of The Magic Circle. Coming in 2019 to PC, PS4, and Xbox One.
|
